<lab name="OSPF_MultiArea" id="6dfa10e7-146b-40d7-bcc4-0ea814838122" version="1" scripttimeout="300" lock="0" author="Shahnawaz">
  <description>This lab demonstrates OSPF multi-area configuration
including DR/BDR election.</description>
  <body>1. Configure OSPF Area 0
2. Configure Area 1 and Area 2
3. Verify DR/BDR election
4. Test connectivity</body>
